org.odk.collect.android.forms

Interface FormSource

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    OpenRosaFormSource

    public interface FormSource
    A place where forms live (outside the app's storage). Ideally in future this would be a common interface for getting forms from a server, Google Drive or even the disk.
